 with Your wisdom and will, and examined us with Your commands and preventions, You provided us means of success and blessed us with different apparatuses, made us obligated according to our ability, and made Your obedience mandatory on us, You commanded us but gave us the free will for obedience, and You warned us and prevented us, gave us enormous bounties but asked for little in return, Your command was disobeyed but You endured, Your position was ignored but You remained beneficent.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ اَنْتَ الْاَوَّلُ بِلَا اَوَّلِیَّۃٍ مَّعْدُوْدَۃٍ، وَالْآخِرُ بِلَا آخِرِیَّۃٍ مَحْدُوْدَۃٍ، اَنْشَاتَنَا لَا لِعِلَّۃٍ اقْتِسَارًا، وَاخْتَرَعْتَنَا لَا لِحَاجَۃٍ اقْتِدَارًا، وَابْتَدَعْتَنَا بِحِكْمَتِكَ اخْتِیَارًا، وَبَلَوْتَنَا بِاَمْرِكَ وَنَهْیِكَ اخْتِبَارًا، وَاَیَّدْتَنَا بِالْآلَاتِ، وَمَنَحْتَنَا بِالْاَدَوَاتِ، وَكَلَّفْتَنَا الطّٰاقَۃَ، وَجَشَّمْتَنَا الطَّاعَۃَ، فَاَمَرْتَ تَخْیِیْرًا، وَنَهَیْتَ تَحْذِیْرًا، وَخَوَّلْتَ كَثِیْرًا، وَسَاَلْتَ یَسِیْرًا فَعُصِیَ اَمْرُكَ فَحَلُمْتَ، وَجُهِلَ قَدْرُكَ فَتَكَرَّمْتَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016453, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Thus You are the Master and the Holder of dignity and mightiness, greatness and loftiness, graciousness and benevolence, kindness and mercifulness, You faithful to Your promise and loyalty, our hearts cannot access Your reality and origin, ideas and thoughts cannot understand Your attributes, none of Your creations is similar to You, and none of Your inventions can be alike You, You are so great that You cannot be sensed, nor touched, nor contacted by the five senses, and how can a creation attain its creator? O Allah, You are much mightier and loftier than what the transgressors say.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "فَاَنْتَ رَبُّ الْعِزَّۃِ وَالْبَهَائِ، وَالْعَظَمَۃِ وَالْكِبْرِیَائِ، وَالْاِحْسَانِ وَالنَّعْمَائِ، وَالْمَنِّ وَالْآلَائِ، وَالْمِنَحِ وَالْعَطَائِ، وَالْاِنْجَازِ وَالْوَفَائِ، وَلَا تُحِیْطُ الْقُلُوْبُ لَكَ بِكُنْۃٍ، وَلَا تُدْرِكُ الْاَوْهَامُ لَكَ صِفَۃً، وَلَا یُشَبِّهُكَ شَیْءٌ مِنْ خَلْقِكَ، وَلَا یُمَثَّلُ بِكَ شَیْءٌ مِنْ صَنْعَتِكَ، تَبَارَكْتَ اَنْ تُحَسَّ اَوْ تُمَسَّ اَوْ تُدْرِ كَكَ الْحَوَاسُّ الْخَمْسُ، وَاَنّٰی یُدْرِكُ مَخْلُوْقٌ خَالِقَهٗ، وَتَعَالَیْتَ یَا اِلٰهِیْ عَمَّا یَقُوْلُ الظّٰالِمُوْنَ عُلُوًّا كَبِیْرًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016454, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, give dominance and victory to Your friends over Your enemies, the oppressors, the transgressors, the oath-breakers, the tyrants and the outlaws, those enemies who misguide Your slaves, distort Your book, alter Your rules, deny Your right, crowd the sittings of Your friends with absolute audaciousness and mischief, and performed this in order to oppress the Holy Progeny of Your Prophet (may Allah send His peace, mercy and blessings upon them). With this act, they proved their misguidance, misguided the people, and tore the veils of Your sanctity from Your slaves.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰھُمَّ اَدِلْ لِاَوْلِیَائِكَ مِنْ اَعْدَائِكَ الظّٰالِمِیْنَ الْبَاغِیْنَ النَّاكِثِیْنَ الْقَاسِطِیْنَ الْمَارِقِیْنَ، اَلَّذِیْنَ اَضَلُّوْا عِبِادَكَ، وَحَرَّفُوْا كِتَابِكَ، وَبَدَّلُوْا اَحْكَامَكَ، وَ