cBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016455, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, these disgraceful enemies took Your assets as their own possession, and made Your slaves and maids as their own. O Allah, they ignored the knowers and scholars of Your land in a state of dumbness, deafness, darkness and corruption. In this way, such a situation came into being that their eyes were open and they could gaze but their hearts went blind. O Allah, there isn’t any proof that you haven’t made apparent for them, You frightened them of Your punishment and warned them of Your reprimand, and promised the obedient ones Your good, and sent forth Your precursors towards them and warned them of Your punishment.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "وَاتَّخَذُوا اللّٰهُمَّ مَالَكَ دُوَلًا، وَعِبَادَكَ خَوَلًا، وَتَرَكُوا اللّٰهُمَّ عَالِمَ اَرْضِكَ فِیْ بَكْمَائَ عَمْیَائَ ظَلْمَائَ مُدْلَهِمَّۃً، فَاَعْیُنُهُمْ مَفْتُوْحَۃٌ، وَقُلُوْبُهُمْ عَمِیَّۃٌ، وَلَمْ تُبْقِ لَهُمُ اللّٰهُمَّ عَلَیْكَ مِنْ حُجَّۃٍ، لَقَدْ حَذَّرْتَ اللّٰھُمَّ عَذَابَكَ۔ وَبَیَّنْتَ نَكَالَكَ، وَ وَعَدْتَ الْمُطِیْعِیْنَ اِخْسَانَكَ، وَقَدَّمْتَ اِلَیْهِمْ بِالنُّذُرِ فَآمَنَتْ طٰائِفَۃٌ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "