Description": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Thus, O Allah, assist the believers against Your enemies and the enemies of Your noble ones, so that they dominate and overcome them, and be the inviters towards truth, and be the followers of the awaited Imam who will rise and establish truth and justice in the world. O Allah, keep on freshening the Hellfire and Your punishment, which You shall not distance from the transgressors, upon Your enemies and the enemies of the Holy Progeny (a.s).", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "فَاَیِّدِ اللّٰھُمَّ الَّذِیْنَ آمِنُوْا عَلٰی عَدُوِّكَ وَعَدُوِّ اَوْلِیَئِكَ، فَاَصْبَحُوْا ظٰاهِرِیْنَ، وَاِلَی الْحَقِّ دَاعِیْنَ، وَلِلْاِمَامِ الْمُنْتَظَرِ الْقَائِمِ بِالْقِسْطِ تَابِعِیْنَ، وَجَدِّدِ اللّٰھُمَّ عَلٰی اَعْدَائِكَ وَاَعْدَائِهِمْ نَارَكَ وَعَذَابَكَ، اَلَّذِیْ لَا تَدْفَعُهٗ عَنِ الْقَوْمِ الظَّالِمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11"